msgstr ""
":ref:`Yksilöllinen koodi tekstiviestillä <sign/security/authentication-sms>`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/sign/security_authentication.rst:100
msgid ""
":ref:`Via Aadhar eSign <sign/security/authentication-aadhaar>` (available in "
"India)"
msgstr ""
":ref:`Aadhar eSign -palvelun kautta <sign/security/authentication-aadhaar>` "
