msgstr ""
"Valitse valikkoriviltä :menuselection:`Lisää -->` :icon:`oi-view-pivot` "
":menuselection:`Pivot-taulukko` :icon:`fa-caret-right` :menuselection:`Odoo-"
"tiedoista`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/spreadsheet/insert/insert_pivot_table.rst:247
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`New Odoo Pivot` panel at the right of the sheet, select "
"the :guilabel:`Model` from which data should be retrieved, then "
"click :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"Valitse taulukon oikealla puolella olevasta :guilabel:`Uusi Odoo Pivot` -"
"paneelista :guilabel:`Malli`, josta tiedot haetaan, ja napsauta sitten "
":guilabel:`Tallenna`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/spreadsheet/insert/insert_pivot_table.rst:250
msgid ""
"A new sheet opens with an empty pivot table in the top-left corner of the "
"sheet; the sheet name is the model name followed by the :ref:`pivot table ID "
"<spreadsheet/pivot-tables/properties-id>`, e.g., *Sales Order (Pivot #1)*. "
"By default, the pivot table is a :ref:`dynamic pivot table <spreadsheet/"
"insert-pivot-table/static-vs-dynamic>`, where the top-left cell contains "
"an :ref:`Odoo-specific array function <spreadsheet/insert-pivot-table/"
"dynamic-function>` that retrieves data from your database "
"once :ref:`columns, rows, and measures have been added <spreadsheet/pivot-"
"tables/build-manipulate>`."
msgstr ""
"Avautuu uusi taulukko, jossa on tyhjä pivot-taulukko taulukon vasemmassa "
"yläkulmassa; taulukon nimi on mallin nimi, jota seuraa :ref:`pivot-taulukon "
"tunniste <spreadsheet/pivot-tables/properties-id>`, esim. *Myyntitilaus "
"(Pivot #1)*. Oletusarvoisesti pivot-taulukko on :ref:`dynaaminen pivot-"
"taulukko <spreadsheet/insert-pivot-table/static-vs-dynamic>`, jossa vasemman "
"yläkulman solu sisältää :ref:`Odoo-spesifisen taulukkofunktion <spreadsheet/"
"insert-pivot-table/dynamic-function>`, joka hakee tiedot tietokannastasi, "
"kun :ref:`sarakkeet, rivit ja mittarit on lisätty <spreadsheet/pivot-tables/"
"build-manipulate>`."

